issue.body:
**Description**: Describe your changes.
- Made the test data driven, so that each model is tested in a separate test case, gives better log output  
- Skipped tests are now visible on the test console log, this will help identify skipped tests for fix
- Made the test output verbosity level to normal, individual tests are shown 

**Motivation and Context**
- Why is this change required? What problem does it solve?
- If it fixes an open issue, please link to the issue here.
